# TWO post-spread cond-attrs forcing the SAME URL-classified name (formaction)
# must build the bag-extraction suppression guard in SOURCE ORDER, not map
# iteration order. The guard is `!<bool-of-first> && !<bool-of-second>` and MUST
# be byte-identical across regenerations (generate idempotence / content-hash
# caching). Ranging the postRuns map here made the two `!bool` terms flip order
# between runs. Render: either branch taken forces its value (extraction
# suppressed); neither taken renders the bag's SANITIZED copy.
